source.name: Average Interest Rate for Treasury Securities
source.description: This dataset shows the average interest rates for U.S Treasury securities for the most recent month compared with the same month of the previous year.    The data is broken down by the various marketable and non-marketable securities.    The summary page for the data provides links for monthly reports from 2001 through the current year. Average Interest Rates are calculated on the total unmatured interest-bearing debt. The average interest rates for total marketable, total non-marketable and total interest-bearing debt do not include the U.S. Treasury Inflation-Protected Securities.
